txt.en: An Ordâkhai champion comes forth to challenge you!
You have defeated the Ordâkhai attacking the people of Gha Nêkha and their captain, Upóha.
Defeat the Ordâkhai bullying the people of Gha Nêkha.
A band of Ordâkhai have invaded Gha Nêkha and are attacking the locals.
'Who are you, that slays my men?'
'Fight me têshu, so I can end you!'
'Today you have saved the people of Gha Nêkha. Well, most of them anyway. Come, let us return to Iridír.'
You have reclaimed Gha Nêkha for the people. The Ordâkhai captain has come forth to challenge you. You should answer his challenge.
'Thank you for you for helping the people of Gha Nêkha, [placeholder]!
